      "text": "Palew-- Padew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Padew is-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] the state was Krakow.",
